title: Fantasy Football Week 13: The push for the playoffs (Podcast)
itunes:title: Fantasy Football Week 13: The push for the playoffs (Podcast)
description:
Michael Barr, Rich Trueman and Damian Sassower break down the final week of the fantasy football season. We discuss who you should pick up on the waiver wire, how to recover from a covid-19 week 12 and the best way to position your team for the playoffs.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
